data.description: Welcome Home!! This Adorable brick ranch has 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and tons of original qualities that have been maintained! The charm is unparalleled. So many updates have been completed to make this property into the PERFECT home for its new owner. Some of the updates include updated electrical, plumbing, new water heater, fresh paint and ceiling fans. Both bathrooms are newly renovated with floor to ceiling ceramic tile, new toilets, w/ sinks, lights & plumbing fixtures. The hardwood flooring in each bedroom, hall & living room has been refinished. Brand new doors and door frames. New LVP has been installed in the den which can be used as a 4th bedroom! The kitchen is spacious with new cabinets & BRAND NEW appliances, glass backsplash and granite countertops. The backyard is fully fenced in and has an oversized covered patio with a NEW METAL ROOF. The new washer & dryer will also convey with the home. There's so much to love about this home! Schedule your showing today.
